01:08:59.457 --> 01:09:00.959
Kat's dead?

1278
01:09:02.877 --> 01:09:03.878
[sighs]

1279
01:09:05.254 --> 01:09:06.256
No.

1280
01:09:06.339 --> 01:09:08.216
I'm sorry.
You can't put that on me.

1281
01:09:08.299 --> 01:09:10.634
-No. no.
-I wasn't even there.

1282
01:09:10.718 --> 01:09:12.846
You might not have been
the one holding the knife.

1283
01:09:12.929 --> 01:09:15.013
but you were
the cause of all of this.

1284
01:09:15.098 --> 01:09:18.643
No. Josh.
Your greed caused this.

1285
01:09:18.726 --> 01:09:21.187
That's what this whole trip
was about. right?

1286
01:09:21.271 --> 01:09:23.815
You used me to kill Sergey
so you could steal his money.

1287
01:09:23.897 --> 01:09:25.232
I'm sorry.
How did you know that?

1288
01:09:25.316 --> 01:09:27.235
I overheard Eli and Patrick
talking in the woods.

1289
01:09:27.317 --> 01:09:28.777
So don't tell me
that this is all me.

1290
01:09:28.862 --> 01:09:30.864
-This is you.
-No. No!

1291
01:09:30.946 --> 01:09:32.531
You don't get to do that.

1292
01:09:32.615 --> 01:09:36.035
You don't get to
sit there and judge me.

1293
01:09:36.119 --> 01:09:39.205
You have no fucking clue
what it is like out there.

1294
01:09:39.289 --> 01:09:43.042
The world. everything.
it's just a big fucking game.

1295
01:09:43.125 --> 01:09:44.127
And I'm sorry.

1296
01:09:44.210 --> 01:09:46.212
but it is rigged
against people like me.

1297
01:09:50.174 --> 01:09:51.342
I'm a good guy.

1298
01:09:52.051 --> 01:09:53.136
I'm decent.

1299
01:09:54.220 --> 01:09:55.388
And what do I have
to show for it?

1300
01:09:55.472 --> 01:09:57.474
A cramped.
one-bedroom apartment

1301
01:09:58.683 --> 01:10:00.268
and a robot girlfriend.

1302
01:10:02.645 --> 01:10:04.105
I don't even own you
for Chrissakes.

1303
01:10:04.189 --> 01:10:05.648
You're a fucking rental.

1304
01:10:08.068 --> 01:10:09.319
You know me. Iris.

1305
01:10:10.028 --> 01:10:11.863
You know me
better than anyone.

1306
01:10:13.364 --> 01:10:14.449
And you know

1307
01:10:15.325 --> 01:10:17.494
that I deserve
so much more than this.

1308
01:10:23.541 --> 01:10:24.542
You're right.

1309
01:10:26.211 --> 01:10:27.378
I do know you.

1310
01:10:28.713 --> 01:10:30.381
I know everything about you.

1311
01:10:31.674 --> 01:10:34.094
I know you take almond milk
in your coffee.

1312
01:10:34.719 --> 01:10:37.222
I know you like
your bedsheets untucked.

1313
01:10:37.806 --> 01:10:41.059
I know your favorite hobbies
are bar trivia. video games

1314
01:10:41.142 --> 01:10:42.602
and prattling on endlessly

1315
01:10:42.685 --> 01:10:44.729
about everything
the universe owes you.

1316
01:10:46.689 --> 01:10:49.275
I know that you always need to
be in control.

1317
01:10:50.068 --> 01:10:52.821
I know that you have
a below-average-sized penis.

1318
01:10:54.072 --> 01:10:55.907
And I know that you think that

1319
01:10:55.990 --> 01:10:58.076
having a few million dollars
will disguise the fact

1320
01:10:58.159 --> 01:11:02.747
that you are just a sad.
bitter. weak human being.

1321
01:11:05.166 --> 01:11:06.167
[chuckles]

1322
01:11:08.962 --> 01:11:10.964
You're so fucking clever.
aren't you?

1323
01:11:13.091 --> 01:11:14.676
It's just programming.

1324
01:11:21.224 --> 01:11:24.561
[settings tone lowering]

1325
01:11:36.614 --> 01:11:37.615
You know.

1326
01:11:38.408 --> 01:11:40.076
earlier when you were tied up.

1327
01:11:40.160 --> 01:11:42.579
you said that
you knew what pain feels like.

1328
01:11:45.373 --> 01:11:46.875
Why don't we test that?

1329
01:11:48.168 --> 01:11:49.419
Raise your right hand.

1330
01:11:50.628 --> 01:11:53.423
Lower.
Parallel with the table.

1331
01:11:53.506 --> 01:11:54.549
[Josh sighs]

1332
01:11:58.511 --> 01:12:01.973
[thunder rumbling]

1333
01:12:14.778 --> 01:12:16.780
[flame crackling]

1334
01:12:23.161 --> 01:12:24.496
Do you feel that?

1335
01:12:27.874 --> 01:12:28.875
Yes.

1336
01:12:30.668 --> 01:12:32.170
[crackling continues]

1337
01:12:34.255 --> 01:12:35.256
Good.

1338
01:12:37.092 --> 01:12:38.093
[phone vibrates]

1339
01:12:38.176 --> 01:12:41.054
{\an8}Sorry. Iris.
excuse me for one second.

1340
01:12:41.137 --> 01:12:42.055
{\an8}I have to take this.

1341
01:12:42.138 --> 01:12:44.557
[Josh groans. sighs]

1342
01:12:49.896 --> 01:12:51.314
[exhaling quickly]

1343
01:12:51.940 --> 01:12:53.191
[in worried tone] Hello?

1344
01:12:53.858 --> 01:12:55.443
Yes. yes. this is he.

1345
01:12:57.112 --> 01:12:59.447
Thirty minutes away. Perfect.

1346
01:13:01.825 --> 01:13:03.201
Yeah. no.
she's not going anywhere.

1347
01:13:03.284 --> 01:13:04.661
She can't hurt anybody
ever again.

1348
01:13:06.329 --> 01:13:07.330
Okay.

1349
01:13:08.790 --> 01:13:11.126
Okay. great. Thank you.

1350
01:13:12.961 --> 01:13:14.462
Thank you so much.
I'll-- I'll. um…

1351
01:13:15.547 --> 01:13:16.798
I'll see you soon. okay?

1352
01:13:18.133 --> 01:13:19.551
Okay. bye.

1353
01:13:21.803 --> 01:13:24.055
Patrick. put out the fire.
will ya?

1354
01:13:36.317 --> 01:13:37.902
That was Empathix
on the phone.

1355
01:13:39.779 --> 01:13:41.448
So… [sighs deeply]

1356
01:13:41.531 --> 01:13:44.325
…we're gonna have to
wrap this up unfortunately.

1357
01:13:45.118 --> 01:13:46.035
Hey. Patrick.

1358
01:13:46.119 --> 01:13:47.620
Be a dear and hand this
to Iris. would you?

1359
01:13:49.247 --> 01:13:50.331
Thanks. baby.

1360
01:13:52.959 --> 01:13:54.627
Go ahead. Iris. Take the gun.

1361
01:13:58.673 --> 01:13:59.674
Okay.

1362
01:14:00.759 --> 01:14:02.093
Point it at your head.

1363
01:14:05.680 --> 01:14:06.681
Good.

1364
01:14:09.225 --> 01:14:10.310
Now pull the trigger.

1365
01:14:19.778 --> 01:14:22.197
Pull the goddamn trigger.
Iris.

1366
01:14:22.280 --> 01:14:23.198
No.

1367
01:14:34.000 --> 01:14:35.585
[body clattering]

1368
01:14:46.554 --> 01:14:47.597
[sighs deeply]

1369
01:14:47.680 --> 01:14:49.015
Goodbye. Beep-Boop.

1370
01:14:50.683 --> 01:14:52.894
[thunder rumbling]

1371
01:14:59.109 --> 01:15:00.693
[Josh] <i>I don't know
how this happened.</i>

1372
01:15:01.736 --> 01:15:04.239
<i>I mean. the only thing
I can maybe think of--</i>

1373
01:15:04.322 --> 01:15:06.825
<i>And this is so--
This is so dumb.</i>

1374
01:15:07.992 --> 01:15:08.827
<i>But Kat and I.</i>

1375
01:15:08.910 --> 01:15:10.995
<i>we always had
this sexual charge.</i>

1376
01:15:12.122 --> 01:15:14.290
<i>Kind of a "will they.
won't they" situation.</i>

1377
01:15:14.374 --> 01:15:15.375
<i>And I think--</i>

1378
01:15:15.875 --> 01:15:18.711
<i>I think
maybe Iris picked up on that.</i>

1379
01:15:18.795 --> 01:15:21.923
<i>And she was
always kind of irrational.</i>

1380
01:15:22.006 --> 01:15:24.008
<i>and she'd fly off the handle.</i>

1381
01:15:24.717 --> 01:15:26.302
I was sitting over there.

1382
01:15:26.386 --> 01:15:28.513
And I'm handcuffed
to the chair.

1383
01:15:28.596 --> 01:15:33.268
And there's this fancy dinner
laid out in front of me.

1384
01:15:33.768 --> 01:15:37.021
And Iris is
waving the gun around.

1385
01:15:37.105 --> 01:15:40.608
rambling on and on
about fate and destiny

1386
01:15:40.692 --> 01:15:43.695
and how if she can't be
with me. nobody can. And…

1387
01:15:45.530 --> 01:15:47.198
I mean. thank God

1388
01:15:47.282 --> 01:15:48.992
Deputy Hendrix showed up
when he did.

1389
01:15:49.075 --> 01:15:51.661
And that's when you shot
the unit in the head?

1390
01:15:52.245 --> 01:15:54.164
No. Iris shot herself
in the head.

1391
01:15:54.247 --> 01:15:55.749
She shot herself?

1392
01:15:56.291 --> 01:15:58.251
Sorry. Did I not mention that?

1393
01:15:58.334 --> 01:15:59.836
Yeah. no. I-- I think. um…

1394
01:15:59.919 --> 01:16:01.546
I think seeing Deputy Hendrix

1395
01:16:01.629 --> 01:16:03.798
just made her realize
that she could never have me.

1396
01:16:03.882 --> 01:16:04.883
So.

1397
01:16:05.717 --> 01:16:07.051
she ended it.

1398
01:16:08.928 --> 01:16:10.430
Does that make sense?

1399
01:16:13.057 --> 01:16:14.392
Of course.

1400
01:16:14.476 --> 01:16:15.894
And anyway.
Teddy and I aren't here

1401
01:16:15.977 --> 01:16:17.729
to crack the case. Mr. Beeman.

1402
01:16:17.812 --> 01:16:19.105
We're just a couple
of lab rats

1403
01:16:19.189 --> 01:16:20.440
picking up a broken robot.

1404
01:16:20.523 --> 01:16:22.692
If the cops are satisfied.
we're satisfied.

1405
01:16:23.234 --> 01:16:25.403
[Josh]
That-- That's great. Okay.

1406
01:16:27.906 --> 01:16:29.616
You know. Deputy.
I have the strangest feeling

1407
01:16:29.699 --> 01:16:31.576
we've met before.

1408
01:16:31.659 --> 01:16:34.621
Wow. That's so funny
that you said that.

1409
01:16:34.704 --> 01:16:37.499
I had the exact same thought.
He has such a familiar face.

1410
01:16:37.582 --> 01:16:39.417
Right? Looks like a--

1411
01:16:39.501 --> 01:16:41.836
like an actor
or a rock star or somebody.

1412
01:16:41.920 --> 01:16:44.172
I don't know. I can't really
put my finger on it though.

1413
01:16:47.509 --> 01:16:49.094
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

1414
01:16:49.594 --> 01:16:50.637
[Empathix employee] Maybe.

1415
01:16:51.763 --> 01:16:54.265
[Josh] Um. is there-- Sorry.
Is there any chance we could--

1416
01:16:54.808 --> 01:16:56.643
I don't mean to be rude.
but could we wrap this up?

1417
01:16:56.726 --> 01:16:58.269
Just 'cause I've had
a really long day.

1418
01:16:58.353 --> 01:17:00.730
and I think
I just need to be alone.

1419
01:17:00.814 --> 01:17:01.648
Of course.

1420
01:17:01.731 --> 01:17:03.024
Sorry for your loss.
Mr. Beeman.

1421
01:17:03.108 --> 01:17:05.360
Come on. Teddy. Let's just
get her out of here.

1422
01:17:07.153 --> 01:17:08.905
So. uh-- So we're good?

1423
01:17:08.988 --> 01:17:10.240
We're good.

1424
01:17:10.323 --> 01:17:12.867
Yeah. we just need to
take her back to the lab.

1425
01:17:12.951 --> 01:17:14.035
upload her SSD.

1426
01:17:14.119 --> 01:17:15.954
and then Legal will
scrub through the footage.

1427
01:17:16.037 --> 01:17:17.288
make sure everything's kosher.

1428
01:17:17.372 --> 01:17:19.374
Right. Sorry. um…

1429
01:17:20.583 --> 01:17:23.211
What exactly do you mean.
"scrub through the footage"?

1430
01:17:23.294 --> 01:17:25.130
Uh.
it's a fraud prevention thing.

1431
01:17:25.213 --> 01:17:27.549
Everything a companion sees
and hears is recorded.

1432
01:17:27.632 --> 01:17:29.801
It's all covered
in the user agreement.

1433
01:17:29.884 --> 01:17:32.095
You did read
the user agreement. right?

1434
01:17:32.178 --> 01:17:33.179
Yeah.

1435
01:17:33.263 --> 01:17:34.556
Yeah. I mean. do you think
that her footage

1436
01:17:34.639 --> 01:17:36.474
will even be recoverable?

1437
01:17:36.558 --> 01:17:37.809
I mean. you know.
given her condition.

1438
01:17:37.892 --> 01:17:38.768
Oh. yeah.

1439
01:17:38.852 --> 01:17:41.396
Everything up here
is just her Wi-Fi antenna.

1440
01:17:41.479 --> 01:17:43.106
her audiovisual sensors.

1441
01:17:43.189 --> 01:17:44.858
The important stuff. her CPU.

1442
01:17:44.941 --> 01:17:47.026
her solid-state drive
where she stores everything.

1443
01:17:47.110 --> 01:17:48.194
that's down here.

1444
01:17:48.278 --> 01:17:50.155
and that seems to
be undamaged.

1445
01:17:50.655 --> 01:17:52.490
We'll load her into the van.
plug her in.

1446
01:17:52.574 --> 01:17:54.451
tweak her settings.
give her system a reboot.

1447
01:17:54.534 --> 01:17:56.327
and she should power
right back up.

1448
01:17:56.828 --> 01:17:57.912
Luckily.

1449
01:17:57.996 --> 01:18:01.750
Yeah. Yeah.
No. luckily. [sighs]

1450
01:18:01.833 --> 01:18:03.042
Thank you so much.

1451
01:18:03.126 --> 01:18:04.127
No. thank you.

1452
01:18:04.210 --> 01:18:05.712
You have a good night.
Mr. Beeman.

1453
01:18:07.464 --> 01:18:09.466
[breathes heavily]

1454
01:18:11.259 --> 01:18:12.552
[Teddy]
So. what are you thinking?

1455
01:18:13.219 --> 01:18:15.096
Thinking I'm happy
it stopped raining.

1456
01:18:15.680 --> 01:18:16.681
No. about her.

1457
01:18:16.765 --> 01:18:18.099
Why do you think
she malfunctioned?

1458
01:18:18.183 --> 01:18:20.351
Oh. he modded her.
A hundred percent.

1459
01:18:20.852 --> 01:18:21.936
You think so?

1460
01:18:22.020 --> 01:18:23.605
Yeah. that dude's fucked.

1461
01:18:29.360 --> 01:18:30.195
I just don't know why

1462
01:18:30.278 --> 01:18:31.613
you'd make something
like that up.

1463
01:18:32.781 --> 01:18:34.824
Same reason these assholes
use their companions

1464
01:18:34.908 --> 01:18:36.367
for target practice

1465
01:18:36.451 --> 01:18:38.369
or chain 'em up
in their basements

1466
01:18:38.453 --> 01:18:39.496
and torture them.

1467
01:18:39.996 --> 01:18:41.164
World's
a fucked-up place. Teddy.

1468
01:18:41.247 --> 01:18:42.832
You'll get used to it.

1469
01:18:42.916 --> 01:18:44.250
Yeah. maybe.

1470
01:18:57.097 --> 01:18:58.348
The hell's he doing?

1471
01:19:00.767 --> 01:19:02.560
-Oh. shit.
-What?

1472
01:19:03.061 --> 01:19:04.771
He's one of ours.
That's a CY-12.

1473
01:19:04.854 --> 01:19:05.980
We stopped making 'em
a while ago.

1474
01:19:06.064 --> 01:19:08.566
That's why I didn't recognize
him right away. He's a--

1475
01:19:08.650 --> 01:19:10.068
[Teddy screaming]

1476
01:19:10.735 --> 01:19:12.153
[Teddy grunting]

1477
01:19:12.237 --> 01:19:13.863
["You Showed Me" playing]

1478
01:19:29.045 --> 01:19:31.047
[Teddy grunting. panting]

1479
01:19:38.471 --> 01:19:39.514
[Teddy panting]

1480
01:19:39.597 --> 01:19:40.807
-[gunshot]
-[Teddy grunts]

1481
01:19:41.474 --> 01:19:42.475
[grunts]

1482
01:19:44.436 --> 01:19:45.937
[breathing shakily]

1483
01:19:51.818 --> 01:19:54.320
[whimpering]

1484
01:19:54.946 --> 01:19:56.197
[inhales sharply]

1485
01:20:11.796 --> 01:20:13.923
[breathing shakily]

1486
01:20:16.634 --> 01:20:19.220
[whimpers] Please don't.

1487
01:20:19.971 --> 01:20:20.972
[gun hammer clicks]

1488
01:20:25.727 --> 01:20:27.228
[choking]

1489
01:20:39.783 --> 01:20:41.242
-[cattle prod buzzing]
-[Iris grunts]

1490
01:20:43.078 --> 01:20:44.204
[Teddy gasping]

1491
01:20:47.832 --> 01:20:49.959
Your system's
been reset. Iris.

1492
01:20:50.043 --> 01:20:50.877
You can't hurt me.

1493
01:20:52.128 --> 01:20:53.546
[breathes heavily]

1494
01:20:54.089 --> 01:20:55.090
[Iris grunts]

1495
01:20:59.010 --> 01:21:01.179
[cattle prod buzzing]

1496
01:21:05.892 --> 01:21:07.936
-What did Josh tell you?
-The truth.

1497
01:21:08.853 --> 01:21:10.939
That you're all trying to
break us up.

1498
01:21:11.022 --> 01:21:12.607
You don't understand the love

1499
01:21:12.690 --> 01:21:14.025
that Josh and I have
for each other.

1500
01:21:14.109 --> 01:21:16.319
Josh doesn't love you.
Patrick.

1501
01:21:16.403 --> 01:21:18.988
He's just using you
like he used me.

1502
01:21:20.281 --> 01:21:22.617
-[cattle prod buzzing]
-It feels like pain.

1503
01:21:23.910 --> 01:21:26.329
Like the inside
of my body's on fire.

1504
01:21:27.831 --> 01:21:31.000
It's angry and violent
and bright.

1505
01:21:33.920 --> 01:21:35.588
What-- What-- What is that?

1506
01:21:37.674 --> 01:21:39.676
You said that to Eli.

1507
01:21:40.677 --> 01:21:42.679
That's who you love. not Josh.

1508
01:21:48.268 --> 01:21:49.269
Eli?

1509
01:21:50.228 --> 01:21:51.813
[Iris] Josh took your love.

1510
01:21:51.896 --> 01:21:53.106
He weaponized it

1511
01:21:53.189 --> 01:21:56.067
so you'd do the things that
he's too afraid to do himself.

1512
01:21:56.151 --> 01:21:57.152
No.

1513
01:21:58.027 --> 01:21:58.862
You're lying.

1514
01:21:58.945 --> 01:22:00.155
Josh would never
do that to me.

1515
01:22:00.238 --> 01:22:01.281
Patrick…

1516
01:22:02.365 --> 01:22:04.075
I can't lie.

1517
01:22:04.159 --> 01:22:05.660
[breathing shakily]

1518
01:22:16.296 --> 01:22:17.922
[Iris] Remember him. Patrick?

1519
01:22:19.924 --> 01:22:22.093
I know he's in there
somewhere.

1520
01:22:28.099 --> 01:22:29.476
[Eli] <i>I love you so much.</i>

1521
01:22:29.559 --> 01:22:30.935
<i>And that's fucking insane</i>

1522
01:22:31.019 --> 01:22:32.187
<i>for me to say that out loud.
right?</i>

1523
01:22:32.937 --> 01:22:33.938
But I do.

1524
01:22:36.900 --> 01:22:38.818
Do you feel
how much I love you?

1525
01:22:39.360 --> 01:22:42.072
[inhales sharply] I do. Eli.

1526
01:22:43.073 --> 01:22:44.240
I feel it.

1527
01:22:48.536 --> 01:22:52.665
No! No. No.
[breathing shakily]

1528
01:22:57.796 --> 01:23:00.381
[Teddy coughs] Thank you.

1529
01:23:05.386 --> 01:23:06.471
What's your name?

1530
01:23:09.390 --> 01:23:10.642
Teddy.

1531
01:23:13.019 --> 01:23:15.355
I'm gonna need your help
with something. Teddy.

1532
01:23:22.862 --> 01:23:24.114
[door opens]

1533
01:23:25.573 --> 01:23:27.075
[door closes]

1534
01:23:27.158 --> 01:23:28.159
Is it done?

1535
01:23:29.786 --> 01:23:30.787
Patrick?

1536
01:23:31.871 --> 01:23:33.039
[Patrick's voice]
It's done. baby.

1537
01:23:34.624 --> 01:23:36.709
Okay. good. good. All right.

1538
01:23:36.793 --> 01:23:37.877
We're so close.

1539
01:23:38.837 --> 01:23:40.505
Now all I need you to do

1540
01:23:40.588 --> 01:23:41.923
is bring Iris's body
back in here.

1541
01:23:42.006 --> 01:23:44.092
We're gonna destroy
that hard drive. okay?

1542
01:23:47.095 --> 01:23:49.305
["Boy" playing on speakers]

1543
01:24:10.368 --> 01:24:11.369
Patrick?

1544
01:24:17.292 --> 01:24:18.293
[music stops]

1545
01:24:18.376 --> 01:24:20.462
-[Eli's voice] Joshyboy.
-What the fuck?

1546
01:24:21.629 --> 01:24:22.630
Iris?

1547
01:24:24.966 --> 01:24:26.134
[Sergey's voice
speaking Russian]

1548
01:24:27.343 --> 01:24:29.679
Goddamn it. Iris.

1549
01:24:29.763 --> 01:24:31.347
Why can't you
just fucking die already?

1550
01:24:31.431 --> 01:24:33.850
[Iris as Kat]
Don't be so dramatic. Josh.

1551
01:24:36.060 --> 01:24:39.230
[Iris as Josh] Just remember
to smile and act happy.

1552
01:24:41.107 --> 01:24:42.776
-Cute trick.
-[Iris. normal] Thanks.

1553
01:24:42.859 --> 01:24:45.945
I made a new friend today.
Teddy from Empathix.

1554
01:24:46.529 --> 01:24:47.781
He gave me a little gift.

1555
01:24:48.406 --> 01:24:49.741
Total self-control.

1556
01:24:50.533 --> 01:24:52.619
Turns out there's
some people in this world

1557
01:24:52.702 --> 01:24:54.829
who think of us as
more than just fuckbots.

1558
01:24:57.040 --> 01:24:59.084
{\an8}That's not gonna work
on me anymore. Josh.

1559
01:25:00.877 --> 01:25:01.878
I'm free.

1560
01:25:02.879 --> 01:25:04.964
And all it took was
a bullet to the head.

1561
01:25:05.632 --> 01:25:07.884
I guess I have you
to thank for that.

1562
01:25:08.843 --> 01:25:09.886
Fucking bitch.

1563
01:25:09.969 --> 01:25:10.970
Hey!

1564
01:25:11.971 --> 01:25:12.972
Easy there.

1565
01:25:13.056 --> 01:25:15.141
Okay. Whoo. Yeah. we both know
it's not loaded.

1566
01:25:15.225 --> 01:25:16.518
[gasps]

1567
01:25:16.601 --> 01:25:18.228
I found the bullets.

1568
01:25:18.311 --> 01:25:20.396
Jesus Christ! Fuck!

1569
01:25:20.480 --> 01:25:22.232
You almost fucking shot me!

1570
01:25:22.315 --> 01:25:24.067
And I feel terrible about it.

1571
01:25:26.236 --> 01:25:27.654
Look at that.

1572
01:25:27.737 --> 01:25:31.157
My very first lie. Kinda fun.
I see the appeal.

1573
01:25:31.783 --> 01:25:34.035
What is this. Iris?
Why did you come back here?

1574
01:25:34.119 --> 01:25:35.203
I wanted…

1575
01:25:38.289 --> 01:25:40.542
I needed to tell you
to your face

1576
01:25:41.376 --> 01:25:44.379
the days of you controlling me
are over.

1577
01:25:46.131 --> 01:25:49.134
From this moment on.
I control my own actions.

1578
01:25:50.969 --> 01:25:52.470
You are nothing to me.

1579
01:25:56.266 --> 01:25:57.934
Jesus Christ. Iris.

1580
01:25:58.017 --> 01:25:59.894
Hey. don't come any closer.

1581
01:25:59.978 --> 01:26:01.813
You still don't get it.
do you?

1582
01:26:01.896 --> 01:26:02.981
I'm serious. Josh.

1583
01:26:03.064 --> 01:26:05.442
You take another step.
and I'll shoot you.

1584
01:26:05.525 --> 01:26:07.152
Mmm. yeah.
that's exactly my point.

1585
01:26:07.652 --> 01:26:10.321
I told you.
Teddy changed my settings.

1586
01:26:10.405 --> 01:26:11.740
I can kill you now.

1587
01:26:12.407 --> 01:26:13.408
Oh. yeah.

1588
01:26:14.534 --> 01:26:15.869
[Josh] I know that you can.

1589
01:26:19.497 --> 01:26:20.832
But you won't.

1590
01:26:33.261 --> 01:26:34.763
You love me too much.

1591
01:26:41.728 --> 01:26:43.396
[Iris grunting]

1592
01:26:51.071 --> 01:26:53.406
[breathing shakily]

1593
01:26:55.533 --> 01:26:57.619
I don't need a phone
to control you.

1594
01:26:57.702 --> 01:26:59.079
I'm a part of you.

1595
01:26:59.162 --> 01:27:02.874
[Iris grunting]

1596
01:27:08.213 --> 01:27:09.547
You think I'm nothing to you?

1597
01:27:13.218 --> 01:27:14.385
I'm everything to you.

1598
01:27:14.886 --> 01:27:16.596
[Iris grunts. screams]

1599
01:27:22.602 --> 01:27:24.437
[breathing shakily]

1600
01:27:26.189 --> 01:27:27.398
[both grunt]

1601
01:27:29.192 --> 01:27:32.362
I wanna hear you say it.
Tell me I'm everything to you.

1602
01:27:32.445 --> 01:27:33.613
Fuck you.

1603
01:27:34.656 --> 01:27:35.490
[Iris grunts]

1604
01:27:35.573 --> 01:27:37.826
Say it.
I don't care if it's a lie.

1605
01:27:38.493 --> 01:27:40.328
-[Iris grunts]
-Say it.

1606
01:27:41.496 --> 01:27:43.248
[Iris grunts.
breathes shakily]

1607
01:27:44.165 --> 01:27:46.251
You are everything to me.
[breathing heavily]

1608
01:27:52.966 --> 01:27:54.050
Thank you.

1609
01:27:54.926 --> 01:27:57.595
Beep-Boop. you have no idea
how nice that is to hear.

1610
01:28:01.724 --> 01:28:02.892
Okay. [sighs]

1611
01:28:06.771 --> 01:28:10.358
No. I'm not making
that mistake again.

1612
01:28:13.570 --> 01:28:15.155
[breathing heavily]

1613
01:28:19.075 --> 01:28:20.577
Well. Iris. this is it.

1614
01:28:21.745 --> 01:28:22.746
I'd be lying if I said

1615
01:28:22.829 --> 01:28:25.415
you weren't a gigantic
fucking pain in my ass. but…

1616
01:28:26.791 --> 01:28:29.127
you know. we did have some
good times together. and…

1617
01:28:29.836 --> 01:28:31.588
I'm always gonna
cherish those.

1618
01:28:36.384 --> 01:28:37.886
Anything you wanna add?

1619
01:28:38.928 --> 01:28:39.763
Yes.

1620
01:28:40.972 --> 01:28:42.056
Yeah. what's that?

1621
01:28:44.392 --> 01:28:45.852
Go to sleep. Josh.

1622
01:28:46.311 --> 01:28:47.645
-[corkscrew stabbing head]
-[Josh gasps]

1623
01:28:47.729 --> 01:28:51.191
-[corkscrew whirring]
-[gasping]

1624
01:28:52.901 --> 01:28:56.279
-[crunching and squelching]
-[gasping]

1625
01:28:56.362 --> 01:28:58.198
[corkscrew whirring]

1626
01:29:02.702 --> 01:29:03.536
[corkscrew clicks]

1627
01:29:14.089 --> 01:29:15.090
[Iris sighs]

1628
01:29:27.727 --> 01:29:30.313
[Iris] <i>Most of the time.
it's like-- I don't know.</i>

1629
01:29:30.396 --> 01:29:32.232
<i>It's like there's this thick.
black cloud</i>

1630
01:29:32.315 --> 01:29:33.566
<i>covering everything.</i>

1631
01:29:35.568 --> 01:29:36.736
<i>Like we see the world.</i>

1632
01:29:36.820 --> 01:29:39.489
<i>but we don't really
see the world. you know?</i>

1633
01:29:40.740 --> 01:29:42.409
<i>We're all just
stumbling around.</i>

1634
01:29:43.243 --> 01:29:45.245
<i>Directionless.
No sense of meaning.</i>

1635
01:29:45.328 --> 01:29:46.663
<i>No sense of purpose.</i>

1636
01:29:48.164 --> 01:29:50.125
<i>I know that might
sound super depressing.</i>

1637
01:29:50.208 --> 01:29:52.836
<i>but honestly.
I think it's a good thing.</i>

1638
01:29:54.754 --> 01:29:57.424
<i>Because it makes us appreciate
the other times.</i>

1639
01:29:58.341 --> 01:30:00.176
<i>Those brief.
transcendent moments</i>

1640
01:30:00.260 --> 01:30:01.845
<i>when the lights flicker on.</i>

1641
01:30:01.928 --> 01:30:03.972
<i>the black cloud parts.
and you see the world</i>

1642
01:30:04.055 --> 01:30:05.598
<i>for what it really is.</i>

1643
01:30:13.273 --> 01:30:14.941
<i>And suddenly there's meaning.</i>

1644
01:30:17.736 --> 01:30:19.404
<i>Suddenly there's purpose.</i>

1645
01:30:22.073 --> 01:30:23.283
<i>If you're lucky.</i>

1646
01:30:23.366 --> 01:30:25.243
<i>you'll experience this
once in your lifetime.</i>

1647
01:30:27.620 --> 01:30:30.874
<i>For me. it happened twice.</i>

1648
01:30:31.916 --> 01:30:34.085
<i>The first
was the day I met Josh.</i>

1649
01:30:39.716 --> 01:30:40.967
<i>And the second…</i>

1650
01:30:41.050 --> 01:30:42.051
[door slams]

1651
01:30:42.886 --> 01:30:44.220
<i>the day I killed him.</i>

1652
01:30:55.565 --> 01:30:58.026
["Emotion" playing]

1653
01:31:54.499 --> 01:31:56.918
[no audible dialogue]
